{"tid":586333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"復課再爆流感　4日38校163人中招","createTime":"2018-03-09T12:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T13:44:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"093b31672c9c30a41cbc1d1736e71774a45929c2","tid":586333,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T12:14:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180309/20326490\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180309%2F20326490&d=kdeg%2BZRbvRkuR6gPxUTO0gdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=4337004f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180309%2F20326490&h=4a09a00c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180309/20326490</a><br />\n<br />\n復課再爆流感　4日38校163人中招<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180309/large/18587412.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180309%2Flarge%2F18587412.jpg&h=d6cb6296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本港至今累積520宗成人及兒童嚴重流感個案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】冬季流感高峯下，小學及幼稚園一度停課，截斷傳播鏈，惟復課後流感爆發情況逐漸回升，周日至前日的4天內，有38間學校及院舍爆發流感，涉及163人，較對上一周全個星期的19宗還要多。<br />\n<br />\n自1月7日踏入流感季節至今，累積539宗院校爆發，當中七成是小學及幼稚園。食物及衞生局局長陳肇始指，難估計流感高峯何時完結，有可能延續到5月，呼籲高危群組接種疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始指出，當局首批加訂的流感疫苗將於月中抵港，而另一批南半球流感疫苗則會於下月抵達。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心最新一期《流感速遞》顯示，前日新增4宗成人嚴重流感個案，另有4人死亡，今年截至前日，已累積520宗成人及兒童嚴重流感個案，當中321人死亡，包括2名兒童。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市民接種逾70萬劑疫苗<br />\n<br />\n此外，衞生防護中心上周收集到的呼吸道樣本中，有21.13%驗出流感病毒，低於前一周的26.17%。乙型流感仍屬主流，佔當中七成；甲型H1流感則佔兩成半。該中心指，最新監測數據反映本地流感活躍程度開始下降，但仍處於高水平，料會持續多一段時間。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始昨日表示，近年市民接種流感疫苗的數字逐年增長，今個流感季節至今，市民已經接種超過70萬劑疫苗，較去年升逾一成。她認為這反映市民打流感針的意識提高，又指如果有需要，政府來年會增加訂購流感針的數目。<br />\n<br />\n■記者袁樂婷"},{"pid":"2a0cfc9ff6fa66afbc9b4c62ad13e7beeb1e1c7b","tid":586333,"uid":174074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T12:16:48.000Z","msg":"當初又講到停課幾咁有效<br />\n病菌受到控制 就算開學都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710deac05aca707d27ce0e186b14f69d5dfa8208","tid":586333,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T12:18:25.000Z","msg":"呢幾日股寒流又會爆一輪"},{"pid":"b1e52c9454218470c450805d01f99e4825d2e53b","tid":586333,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a0cfc9ff6fa66afbc9b4c62ad13e7beeb1e1c7b","tid":586333,"uid":174074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T12:16:48.000Z","msg":"當初又講到停課幾咁有效<br />\n病菌受到控制 就算開學都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T12:21:10.000Z","msg":"咩病菌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f656228268faaec5ae5778f8c793e75617563b29","tid":586333,"uid":174074,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b1e52c9454218470c450805d01f99e4825d2e53b","tid":586333,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a0cfc9ff6fa66afbc9b4c62ad13e7beeb1e1c7b","tid":586333,"uid":174074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T12:16:48.000Z","msg":"當初又講到停課幾咁有效<br />\n病菌受到控制 就算開學都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T12:21:10.000Z","msg":"咩病菌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T12:22:38.000Z","msg":"流感病菌"},{"pid":"7f9314040709ef07b4a1ce64085534e9ac9367ae","tid":586333,"uid":58358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f656228268faaec5ae5778f8c793e75617563b29","tid":586333,"uid":174074,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b1e52c945421